SECTION 1: Project Scope & Data Sources
---------------------------------------
- **What is VOC?**
  - Voice of the Customer (VOC) captures direct feedback, complaints, and suggestions from customers.
  - In call centers, VOC focuses on analyzing complaint data to improve service, satisfaction, and process.
- **Why Analyze Call Center Complaints?**
  - Identifies service gaps, recurring issues, and agent performance.
  - Drives actionable business improvements.

------------------------------

SECTION 2: Data Preparation
---------------------------
- **Step 1:** Collect complaint logs (CSV, Excel, database).
- **Step 2:** Clean data (remove duplicates, fill blanks, standardize categories).
- **Step 3:** Format fields (dates, IDs, complaint types).

