SECTION 3: Analysis & Visualization
-----------------------------------
- **Bar Chart:** Complaint Types (Color bars by category: Billing = blue, Service = orange, Technical = green)
- **Pie Chart:** Resolution Status (Resolved = green, Unresolved = red)
- **Line Chart:** Complaints trend over time (use a vibrant color gradient)

[ðŸ’¡ TIP: In Excel, apply chart styles, bold axis labels, and legend with accent colors.]

------------------------------

SECTION 4: Insights & Recommendations
-------------------------------------
- **Top Complaint Drivers:** Highlight with colored bullet points.
- **Recurring Issues:** Use colored boxes for emphasis.
- **Recommendations:**
  - Provide agent training (highlight in yellow)
  - Improve resolution workflow (highlight in blue)
  - Enhance self-service options (highlight in green)

------------------------------

SECTION 5: PPT Slide Structure
------------------------------
- **Slide 1:** Title (use background gradient or accent color)
- **Slide 2:** Data Overview (icon for call center)
- **Slide 3:** Key Metrics (colorful charts)
- **Slide 4:** Complaint Analysis (bar/pie chart)
- **Slide 5:** Insights & Recommendations (use colored callouts)
- **Slide 6:** Next Steps (colored checklist)

